[4] Saudi Arabia no new cases - MOH 7 Jun 2015
Date: 7 Jun 2015
Source: Saudi MOH [edited]
http://www.moh.gov.sa/en/ccc/pressreleases/pages/default.aspx?PageIndex=1


As of 12 Noon today 7 Jun 2015 there have been a total of:
1026 laboratory confirmed cases of MERS-CoV infection, including
450 deaths,
563 recoveries, and
13 currently active cases including 2 on home isolation.

In the past 24 hours there have been:
0 newly confirmed cases reported,
0 deaths reported, and
0 recoveries reported.

[Reported case fatality rate 43.9 percent]

